Barberton Rugby Club invite all companies to enter their golf and touch rugby days. The golf day will held on Friday November 16 and the touch rugby on Saturday. The golf will be played in a fourball American scramble format, and tee-off is at 10:00 at the Barberton Golf Club. The touch rugby will be played seven-a-side. The first game will start at 08:00 at Coronation Park.
